  "title": "Massage Therapist",
  "description": "<p>We are hiring Massage Therapist.</p>\n<p>Requirement and Benefit</p>\n<p>- Provide consistent professional spa massage in accordance with spa standards.</p>\n<p>- Ensure high level of service standards.</p>\n<p>- Responsible for the maintenance of cleanliness and neatness of the spa facilities, treatment rooms and other parts of the spa.</p>\n<p>- Responsible preparing the necessary treatment products, replenishment of stocks, towels supply etc.</p>\n<p>- Handle customer queries and concerns efficiently and politely</p>\n<p>- Follow and comply with the instructions given by Spa Manager</p>\n<p>- 6 days work weekly</p>\n<p>- Minimum 1 year experience</p>\n<p>- Training is provided</p>\n<p>- Salary 3000 - 5000 with bonus</p>\n<p>If you are interested, kindly contact us at 87226158.</p>",
